clock.template_hint:
Variables:  {time:%H:%M}  {date:%Y.%m.%d}  {weekday}  {tz_label}
Style:  {time:%H:%M|size=36|bold|color=#ff4da6}   |italic   |size=N
Leave empty to use the basic mode.

countdown.template_hint:
Variables:  {remaining}  {target:%Y-%m-%d %H:%M}  {days}  {hours}  {minutes}  {seconds}
Style:  {remaining|size=36|bold|color=#ff4da6}   |italic   |size=N
Leave empty to use the basic mode.

datecard.template_hint:
Variables:  {weekday}  {weekday:short}  {day}  {date:%Y.%m.%d}  {doy}
Style:  {day|size=42|bold|color=#ff4da6}   |italic   |size=N
Leave empty to use the basic mode.

dday.template_hint:
[ Variables ]  {dday}  {days}  {sign}  {label}  {date:%Y.%m.%d}  {date_short}
[ Style ]  {dday|size=60|bold|color=#ff4da6}  {label|size=13|italic}
[ Line break ]  Use \n for multiple lines
[ Empty ]  Basic mode (name + date on two lines)

stopwatch.template_hint:
Variables:  {elapsed}  {elapsed_ms}  {running}
Style:  {elapsed|size=36|bold|color=#ff4da6}   |italic   |size=N
Leave empty to use the basic mode.

widget_text.template_help:
Inline style: {value|size=36|bold|italic|color=#ff4da6}
Line break: \n   e.g. {time:%H:%M|size=36|bold}\n{date|size=12|color=#8090b0}
Condition block: {if task_count > 0}content{else}fallback{/if} (no nesting)
Timezone: {time:tz=JST:%H:%M} / {time:tz=UTC+9:%H:%M}

widget_text.hint_text:
[ Time/Date ]  {time:%H:%M}  {time:tz=JST:%H:%M}  {time:tz=UTC+9:%H:%M}
              {date:%Y.%m.%d}  {weekday}  {weekday:short}
[ Widget Data ]  {stopwatch:stopwatch_0}  {countdown:countdown_0}  {dday:dday_0}
[ D-Day ]  {dday}  (local D-Day value from this widget)
[ App Data ]  {task_count}  {directive_count}  {next_event}  {custom_var}
[ Conditions ]  {if task_count > 0}Tasks {task_count}{else}None{/if}
              {if countdown:countdown_0 < 1h}Due soon{else}Plenty of time{/if}
